Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.xmldb.process

Contains the storage classes that implement a XMLDB version of the Process storage.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IAeProcessConfigKeys An interface that simply holds some static constants which are the names of keys in the XMLDB config object.
IAeProcessElements Constants that define the Process element names.
 

Class Summary
AeXMLDBFilteredProcessListQueryBuilder A filtered process list query builder.
AeXMLDBLogReader Responsible for reading the log for a given process out of the XMLDB database.
AeXMLDBLogReader.AeLogEntry Container class for a clob row.
AeXMLDBLogStreamReader This class is responsible for putting a Reader facade on the process log for a given process.
AeXMLDBProcessStateConnectionProvider A XMLDB implementation of a process state connection provider.
AeXMLDBProcessStateStorageProvider A XMLDB implementation of a process state storage provider.
 

Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.xmldb.process Description

Contains the storage classes that implement a XMLDB version of the Process storage.
